  8248                           ;	WDT operating mode
  8249                           ;	WDTE = OFF, WDT Disabled, SWDTEN is ignored
  8250                           ;	WDT Window Select bits
  8251                           ;	WDTCWS = WDTCWS_7, window always open (100%); software control; keyed access not requi
